  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-04 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level 3. Seven factors are assessed; three factors are flagged not-assessed on grounds that they fall 'beyond the scope of the current submission' — a rationale that is not concretely justified. At MRL 3 the absence of assessed factors for model form, use error, and equivalency of input parameters materially weakens credibility. Decision is recorded as Accepted despite these gaps, instantiating the W-EP-04 weakness pattern.",
